document.full_text: a single-seat f-16 fighter jet from the wisconsin national guard crashed on tuesday while on a routine training mission in central wisconsin, but the pilot ejected safely, the national guard said in a statement.
document.title: wisconsin national guard f-16 jet crashes, pilot safe
